            <thetext>Hi, I miss a true multiple selection mode in the qx.ui.List widget. That is, I want to add new items _without_ holding down the &lt;Control&gt; key. In the Motif terms, it&#39;s XmMULTIPLE_SELECT (while the current qooxdoo implementation is XmEXTENDED_SELECT), see, e.g., &lt;http://linux.die.net/man/3/xmlist&gt;. A patch will follow soon.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
